# 🏥 MyJeevan Health - Enterprise Clinical Command Center

MyJeevan Health is a modern, responsive, and enterprise-grade **Clinical Command Center Dashboard** designed for healthcare facilities. It integrates real-time telemetry, electronic medical records (EMR) management, dynamic ward/bed allocation, and secure cloud database integration for insurance claim auditing using Firebase.

## 🚀 Key Features

- **📊 Master Analytics Dashboard**: Interactive charts showing patient admissions trend and department load distribution (powered by Chart.js).
- **📁 EMR Patient Registry**: Complete diagnostic records, active treatment plans, and live vitals tracking.
- **🛏️ Live Ward & Bed Allocator**: Dynamic system to view, assign, or discharge patients from ICU, CCU, and Emergency wards.
- **📄 Secure Patient Claims System (Firebase-backed)**: A direct portal to push healthcare claims and financial audits to remote Cloud Firestore in real-time.
- **🚨 Real-Time Telemetry Logs & Alerts**: Simulated live monitoring of patient vitals with critical telemetry alerts.
- **🎨 Modern Dark UI**: Crafted using React, Tailwind CSS, and Lucide Icons with fully responsive layouts.

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- **Frontend:** React 18, Tailwind CSS, Lucide Icons
- **Database:** Google Firebase Firestore
- **Charts:** Chart.js

